Nord Resources Corp said KleinwortGrieveson and Co, a U.K. investment banking firm, has agreed toprivately place 600,000 Nord common shares with institutionalinvestors outside of the U.S., primarily in the U.K.    Nord said the placement was priced at 17.50 dlrs a share,90 pct of the stock's closing price yesterday, and is scheduledto close April 10.    The company said it will raise about 10 mln dlrs which willbe used for general corporate purposes. Reuter&#3;